{
  "stem": "9725.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he turned me around to him, and he said, I want your promise right now.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I said, I promise you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, at one point in my life when I came very close to jumping into, into a train after working all day at [NON-ENGLISH] and at some horrible works.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the nights on coal trains, my resistance was really going down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I said, you know, it's the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I'll just jump.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And it will be a few seconds, and it's going to be all over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And at this precise moment, I felt a pain in my neck [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that the promise came back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was and my father always knew what I was thinking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And he made me promise not to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So shortly thereafter, they rescinded the order, and we were permitted to stay again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was sort of going on every six, every seven or eight months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they would come and say, you know, we got an order that we have to leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it would be said that if half a kilo of gold could be produced, we would not have to leave.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you know, everybody gave what they had-- a wedding rings, this and that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people brought in order to stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this, of course, was the way in which they extracted everything that one had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So that was going on for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother got better, as I mentioned, until we moved to the basement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were doing knitting, and we got 30 marks for knitting a sweater, which took us almost a week.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at the black market, you could buy a loaf of bread for about that amount of money.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
